               <lb n="4"/>
               <expan><abbr><num xml:lang="lat" value="11">XI</num>,me</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>sibus</abbr></expan>
               <lb n="5"/>
               <num xml:lang="lat" value="3">III</num>. <persName>
                  <name type="slaveName" key="Irena">Irena</name>
               </persName>
               <lb n="6"/>mater fili
                <lb break="no" n="7"/>o <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan>
               <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan>
               <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan>.</ab>
            <!-- The marked up transcription goes here, surrounded by <ab> </ab> elements -->
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the Divine Spirits. To Firmus, who lived for eleven years (and) three
               months. Irena, (his) mother, made this for (her) son, well-deserving.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Complete inscription attested in <hi rend="italic">CIL</hi> X, 2422a.</p>
